# Testing — Índice global

**Regla:** ningún módulo se mergea sin tests. CI bloquea PR si falla cualquier capa.

## Matriz resumida

| Capa | Rule detalle | Tool | Cov |
|------|--------------|------|-----|
| Backend Python | `python-testing.mdc` | pytest | ≥80% |
| Frontend React | `web-testing.mdc` | Vitest | ≥70% |
| Infra + Docker | `infra-testing.mdc` | bicep + docker | 100% files |
| CI pipeline | `azure-cicd.mdc` | GitHub Actions | — |

## Comando local

```bash
./scripts/run-all-tests.sh
```

## Al agregar código

| Si tocas… | Agrega test en… |
|-----------|-----------------|
| `backend/app/` | `backend/tests/unit/` o `integration/` |
| `backend/scripts/` | `backend/tests/scripts/` |
| `web/src/` | `__tests__/` junto al módulo |
| `infra/` | `infra/tests/validate-modules.sh` |
